  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beat time-trial levels using parkour moves</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/358049191160a71e9fb2b30adf1646f0.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/358049191160a71e9fb2b30adf1646f0.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/358049191160a71e9fb2b30adf1646f0.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Parkour Legends is a 2D platformer with parkour moves where you complete time-trial courses. Vault over obstacles, slide under pathways, run on walls, and rebound over impossible gaps to get the fastest completion times. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is not an auto-runner. It is designed for both Gamepad or Mouse and Keyboard where you control the runner and perform the moves using specific button combinations.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Content</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 250 hand-crafted levels, designed to fully test your skills across all the moves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 goal times per level to strive for</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 20 types of gear in dozens of colors, such as shirts, shorts, gloves, hats and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2 hard-to-reach items and 2 optional objectives for each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customize your runner's hair-style and appearance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Leaderboards for every level</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please Wishlist if you're interested!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/c645dd7356a05bbda5ea83859b7cc83d.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/c645dd7356a05bbda5ea83859b7cc83d.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/c645dd7356a05bbda5ea83859b7cc83d.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlisting the game greatly improves the game's chances of doing well on Steam. So if you're interested or played the free demo and liked it, please please please consider wishlisting. It really makes a huge difference :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parkour moves to master</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sprint, slide, roll, rebound, grab onto ledges, and run across walls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Kongs, tic tacs, lazy vaults. You name it. We got it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Speed boosts after performing vaults</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build up adrenaline with risky moves and sprint to get faster times</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/111a3207a048946be0697d898e381d1a.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/111a3207a048946be0697d898e381d1a.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/111a3207a048946be0697d898e381d1a.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use momentum and speed boosts</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing well and performing tricks rewards you with speed boosts. Use your speed boosts wisely and shave seconds off your time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Decide the best moves and route</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find short cuts and optimal paths using your parkour skills. This is not an auto-runner. It is designed for both <strong>Gamepad</strong> or <strong>Mouse and Keyboard</strong> where you control the runner and perform the moves using specific button combinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect hard-to-reach items</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For extra challenge and fun, there are collectibles in each level that are hard-to-reach, but yield gear you can use to style your runner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/5e4a6d6c26e8faad3d4bca1aee0f22fd.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/5e4a6d6c26e8faad3d4bca1aee0f22fd.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/5e4a6d6c26e8faad3d4bca1aee0f22fd.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't slip up!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must avoid slip-ups and tripping over objects to maintain your momentum. One wrong move can cost you a rank.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/75da190cf6cdf5b029875854109f3768.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/75da190cf6cdf5b029875854109f3768.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/75da190cf6cdf5b029875854109f3768.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb the leaderboards and show off your skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See how your times compare to everyone else in the world. Go for one more run and improve your world-ranking!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your runner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your runner's appearance and hair along with gear and accessories found in hard-to-reach areas and from completing level objectives</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/03f8b4292f6e315ca4eab513904e3a6b.poster.avif?t=1745703838\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/03f8b4292f6e315ca4eab513904e3a6b.webm?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115130/extras/03f8b4292f6e315ca4eab513904e3a6b.mp4?t=1745703838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
